originalText.text: If you run a business you know by now that good service providers are extremely hard to come by. Beyond being one of the most talented photographers and videographers I have had the pleasure of working with, Eyal of Foo-Food is also incredibly dedicated to any project he takes on, and has an awesome energy that makes him super fun to work with! Price is always fair and the turn around time of finished products is extremely fast! 5+ stars.

originalText.text:
There are many creative photographers out there. But Eyal from FOO - FOOD is one of these rare ones that listens and execute what you're looking for, what your brand really needs and not forcing on you his personal style. Add to this amazing customer service, quality and YES!! unbelievable creativity that will show you different angles that you didn't think of and you have best value for money and best photographer you can expect for.. Moving forward Eyal and FOO - FOOD is part of our family and photographer resident.

Oded Brenner - Blue Stripes Cacao Shop (Founder of Max Brenner Chocolate by the Bald Man)

originalText.text: Had collaborated with Eyal, the Creative Director personally. Apart from his strong passion towards visual art, he is also quite sensitive to detail as proven to his food photographs. We had collaborated in few 3D animations, a different territory than where he usually be - videography and photography, and he has been remarkably precise with his ideal vision, yet flexible enough to let you use what you got with you at the time to its finesse, albeit this happened remotely and not face-to-face. Sure enough, in this spring they will probably making use of colorful herbs and flowers again in their photography despite the global lockdown (and few who protest). You should have not wait to request their service, they are very productive to begin with.

originalText.text:
We turned to Foo-Food in the request of using one of its beautiful pictures for a recent nonprofit fundraising campaign.
We received an immediate positive reply.
The selected picture upgraded our campaign and contributed to its elegant and prestigious look.

We are grateful to Foo-Food for their donation and open heartedness.

Honey Maor
Producer
Reuth, Israeli NGO
